	<!-- message -->
	<p>I have to agree on most points stated in this discussion.  I feel we MUST pick the most important issues and go from there.  Simply stating everything we are unhappy about to the most minor detail will only make us look worse.  <br />
<br />
So, I chose 2 areas I feel we need the most improvement on.<br />
<br />
1. Healing - read your neat little EQ handbook that came with the game.  The install blah blah blah.  There is a breakdown of classes in this which states something along the lines of "witchdoctor"   and tribal "healer" as a MAIN ability.  I'll quote this later, perhaps we can send that into Sony and see what they think about it.<br />
<br />
2. Slows - makes me grind my teeth when I think of how contested our slows have become.   This will probably be more difficult to fix than the healing issue but in my mind needs to be addressed jsut as urgently.<br />
<br />
I trust the judgement of the Shamans here and have no objections to suggestions thus far.  I am just casting my vote for what i feel needs priority.</p>
	
	
	
