	<p>I am whole heartedly with this discussion. Primarily in my experience in groups and soloing lead me to agree with Apothian.<br />
<br />
Heals: More often than not I find my self as main or second healer in a group and am hardly ever quite fit for the job. Its not fun for me to constantly canni for 3 hours just to keep MTs alive. We need an upgrade there.<br />
<br />
Slows: In a world where other classes are a mere 5 percent below our "class defining" ability and where end game mobs make it a trivial skill with mitigation, our ability to slow needs to be re-thought.<br />
<br />
Vote cast.</p>
	
	
	
