	<p>We will never, ever, ever agree on what "fix" is right for each problem.<br />
<br />
I think we need to provide:<br />
<br />
1. A detailed bullet list of the problems<br />
Not the fixes, just the problems.<br />
<br />
2. A dialouge that explains each of the above problems in detail, why we think they are broken.<br />
We don't need to provide solutions like "Upgrade our direct heal to 1700", we need to only explain why 1300 is to low.</p>
	
	
	
