	<!-- message -->
	<p>Do you mean, malosinia? Malos is un-resistable (which is what I meant by "quite a resist mod").<br />
<br />
Don't get me wrong, I think it's a great idea for slow in an exp group, but it might be a bit over powering in a raid situation where debuffing the mob prior to slow is an important step. Malos THEN malosinia THEN slow (well, tash and HOS as well). Not to mention, a lot of mages take their malosinia role on raids very seriously. Of course, we malosinia for other reasons besides slow (nukes) so it's not like we wouldn't still have to do it.<br />
<br />
I'm just thinking that it would be TOO good and borders on an unreasonable request.</p>
	
	
	
