	<td class="alt2" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>I see a lot of productive ideas on here, things like upping the damage on the poison nuke/adding a new poison nuke, group Q as an AA or a new spell, etc.....but I also see odd ball things that really dont belong in the game....a Slow that has Malo attached? thats like asking for a flame thrower when your 5; sure its a good idea at the time, but what the hell happens when you get it?<br />
Lets get some realistic ideas here, and no I dont have any, but I think that any ideas that we present to SOE need to be to the point, realistic and time oriented.<br />
We should ask for a ~2k blast heal for 450 mana, Group Q as an AA (IE Paragon/Spirit of Wood) or as a spell, a broad upgrade to Focus and Q (add resists or ATK to Focus and upgrade Q to 350/tick) and a general upgrade to dogdog, either by revamping the level 61 spell, or making a new level 65 spell that summons a level 60 dog that innately dual wields and has a good atk.<br />
Dont ask for Phaser Technology when the best available is .357 Mag revlovers, its tackey and prevents us from getting any upgrades as it makes us seem greedy, full of class envy, and in general as pissers and moaners.</p>
	
	
	
